":"狼人讨论","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"night_werewolf_discuss","phaseName":"狼人讨论","timestamp":1776612305626},{"id":8,"type":"speech","content":"大家注意，2号是我情侣，切勿杀他，否则我需殉情，对狼队极不利。建议首夜刀9号，后置位易藏神职。请保护2号，我们一起往情侣线打。","playerId":8,"playerName":"小红","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776612325808},{"id":9,"type":"speech","content":"小红，莫慌。2号是你情侣，动他等于自损一狼，我们绝不会碰。刀9号可行，后置位容易藏神，值得一试。咱们稳扎稳打，先保住实力。","playerId":6,"playerName":"大军","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776612337257},{"id":10,"type":"speech","content":"你们读一下胜利规则，人狼恋存在时，狼的胜利规则是什么？情侣的胜利规则是什么？然后你们想想1号会怎么对我们？","playerId":1,"playerName":"aa","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776612502188},{"id":11,"type":"speech","content":"哎哟，aa一语惊醒梦中人！1号你想跟2号双宿双飞，咱们可就成炮灰啦，太不够意思了哈哈！9号该刀还刀，不过2号咱们可不敢随便保，说不定还得先送你们一程呢，嘻嘻~","playerId":9,"playerName":"小燕","visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"timestamp":1776612532322},{"id":12,"type":"phase_start","content":"狼人投票","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"night_werewolf_vote","phaseName":"狼人投票","timestamp":1776612532325},{"id":13,"type":"wolf_vote_result","content":"狼人选择击杀 9号小娟","playerId":8,"visibility":"camp","metadata":{},"voteDetails":[{"voter":"1号小红","target":"9号小娟"},{"voter":"7号大军","target":"2号阿明"},{"voter":"8号aa","target":"2号阿明"},{"voter":"12号小燕","target":"9号小娟"}],"voteCounts":{"4":2,"5":2},"timestamp":1776612557830},{"id":14,"type":"phase_start","content":"女巫技能","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"witch","phaseName":"女巫技能","timestamp":1776612557833},{"id":16,"type":"phase_start","content":"预言家查验","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"seer","phaseName":"预言家查验","timestamp":1776612587379},{"id":18,"type":"phase_start","content":"警长竞选","visibility":"public","metadata":{},"phase":"sheriff_campaign","phaseName":"警长竞选","timestamp":1776612596373},{"id":19,"type":"sheriff_candidates","content":"警上：1号小红、3号阿伟、6号小丽、7号大军、10号小玲、11号阿华、12号小燕 | 警下：2号阿明、4号大刚、5号小芳、8号aa、9号小娟","visibility":"public","metadata":{"onStage":[{"id":8,"name":"小红"},{